OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ruth Perry's sister has called Ofsted's
OL,6, response to the verdict of the inquest 
OL,7, into her death "woefully inadequate".  
OL,9,FSenior coroner Heidi Connor ruled on   
OL,10,FThursday that an Ofsted inspection at  
OL,11,FCaversham Primary contributed to the   
OL,12,Fhead teacher taking her own life.      
OL,14,FOfsted chief inspector Amanda Spielman 
OL,15,Fapologised for the distress it had     
OL,16,Fcaused Mrs Perry and said next week's  
OL,17,Finspections would be delayed by a day. 
OL,19,FBut Mrs Perry's sister, Julia Waters,  
OL,20,Fsaid that was "just not enough".       
